{
  "ref": "Psalms 128",
  "heRef": "תהילים קכ״ח",
  "isComplex": false,
  "text": [
    "A song of ascents.<br><span class=\"poetry indentAll\">Happy is any man<sup class=\"footnote-marker\">a</sup><i class=\"footnote\"><b>man </b>Moved up from v. <a class=\"refLink\" data-ref=\"Psalms 128:4\" href=\"Psalms.128.4\">4</a> for clarity.</i> who fears G<small>OD</small>,</span><br><span class=\"poetry indentAllDouble\">who follows godly ways.</span>",
    "<span class=\"poetry indentAll\">You shall enjoy the fruit of your labors;</span><br><span class=\"poetry indentAllDouble\">you shall be happy and you shall prosper.</span>",
    "<span class=\"poetry indentAll\">Your wife shall be like a fruitful vine within your house;</span><br><span class=\"poetry indentAllDouble\">your children, like olive saplings around your table.</span>",
    "<span class=\"poetry indentAll\">So shall all<sup class=\"footnote-marker\">b</sup><i class=\"footnote\"><b>all </b>Moved down from v. <a class=\"refLink\" data-ref=\"Psalms 128:1\" href=\"Psalms.128.1\">1</a> for clarity there.</i> who fear G<small>OD</small> be blessed.</span>",
    "<span class=\"poetry indentAll\">May G<small>OD</small> bless you from Zion;</span><br><span class=\"poetry indentAllDouble\">may you share the prosperity of Jerusalem</span><br><span class=\"poetry indentAllDouble\">all the days of your life,</span>",
    "<span class=\"poetry indentAllDouble\">and live to see your children’s children.</span><br><span class=\"poetry indentAll\">May all be well with Israel!</span>"
  ],
  "he": [
    "שִׁ֗יר הַֽמַּ֫עֲל֥וֹת אַ֭שְׁרֵי כׇּל־יְרֵ֣א יְהֹוָ֑ה הַ֝הֹלֵ֗ךְ בִּדְרָכָֽיו׃",
    "יְגִ֣יעַ כַּ֭פֶּיךָ כִּ֣י תֹאכֵ֑ל אַ֝שְׁרֶ֗יךָ וְט֣וֹב לָֽךְ׃",
    "אֶשְׁתְּךָ֤&thinsp;<b>׀</b> כְּגֶ֥פֶן פֹּרִיָּה֮ בְּיַרְכְּתֵ֢י בֵ֫יתֶ֥ךָ בָּ֭נֶיךָ כִּשְׁתִלֵ֣י זֵיתִ֑ים סָ֝בִ֗יב לְשֻׁלְחָנֶֽךָ׃",
    "הִנֵּ֣ה כִי־כֵ֭ן יְבֹ֥רַךְ גָּ֗בֶר יְרֵ֣א יְהֹוָֽה׃",
    "יְבָרֶכְךָ֥ יְהֹוָ֗ה מִצִּ֫יּ֥וֹן וּ֭רְאֵה בְּט֣וּב יְרוּשָׁלָ֑͏ִם כֹּ֝֗ל יְמֵ֣י חַיֶּֽיךָ׃",
    "וּרְאֵֽה־בָנִ֥ים לְבָנֶ֑יךָ שָׁ֝ל֗וֹם עַל־יִשְׂרָאֵֽל׃&nbsp;<span class=\"mam-spi-pe\">{פ}</span><br>"
  ],
